{"tid":1200113,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[無圖請廣傳]不要自拍打卡，提防Fake News","createTime":"2019-06-10T16:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T05:57:46.000Z","uid":162535,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"29399dd39a8b45cb4ef4515b8ab717cbc34b4c04","tid":1200113,"uid":162535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:19:00.000Z","msg":"小弟廢柴美術JJ一名，自問唔打得，出到去都只可以做後勤，出發之前想做多少少野<br />\n網上廣傳/print出黎當日派通街都ok<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BUFskRn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBUFskRn.jpg&h=e99001fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">防止點相</span></span><br />\n請廣傳<br />\n不要自拍打卡，暴露行程<br />\n不要upload未經處理/人臉照片到任何社交網站，包括Friend Only <br />\n保護自己人<br />\n防止點相 人人有責<br />\nPSD: <a href=\"https://mega.nz/#!NPgVCIjI!LU9Glr0Ida2ZFqStuJhaqvIcFYFZMFc8hSjhMgQf9SM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmega.nz%2F%23%21NPgVCIjI%21LU9Glr0Ida2ZFqStuJhaqvIcFYFZMFc8hSjhMgQf9SM&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=35785781\" target=\"_blank\">https://mega.nz/#!NPgVCIjI!LU9Glr0Ida2ZFqStuJhaqvIcFYFZMFc8hSjhMgQf9SM</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1A9kFZ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1A9kFZ0.jpg&h=081cabaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">提防Fake News</span></span><br />\n不要盡信討論區及通訊apps群組的資訊 <br />\n以現場及可信媒體消息為準<br />\nPSD: <a href=\"https://mega.nz/#!MG52kQgY!uWOZ163fqlr7nGqKXm45oZmKTSR2UJWGbHoiTwCGNTM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmega.nz%2F%23%21MG52kQgY%21uWOZ163fqlr7nGqKXm45oZmKTSR2UJWGbHoiTwCGNTM&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=e5311241\" target=\"_blank\">https://mega.nz/#!MG52kQgY!uWOZ163fqlr7nGqKXm45oZmKTSR2UJWGbHoiTwCGNTM</a><br />\n<br />\n歡迎其他巴絲跟隊做其他文宣/修改<br />\n時間緊逼我就唔再改架喇，有心人可以接力"},{"pid":"5bbd7e0f8e5115f942a877e4b4e0f259544303a5","tid":12